#A  CharacterDegrees( <G> )
#O  CharacterDegrees( <G>, <p> )
#A  CharacterDegrees( <tbl> )
##
##  In the first two forms, `CharacterDegrees' returns a collected list of
##  the degrees of the absolutely irreducible characters of the group <G>;
